id: pm-frou
title: "Scaffolder emits TypeScript: index.ts + tsconfig.json + build script, compiled ./index.js entry"
description: "Rewrite src/cli/commands/extension/scaffold.ts to generate TypeScript source: index.ts (typed activate/deactivate + capability surfaces importing types from @unbrained/pm-cli/sdk), tsconfig.json compiling to ./index.js, and a package.json build script (tsc) + devDependency on typescript. The manifest entry stays ./index.js (compiled output). Mirror the first-party packages/pm-* layout. Keep the colocated sample test as index.test.ts. Update SCAFFOLD_* constants, README bullets/sections, and the define*-builder snippet to TypeScript. 100% line + docstring coverage."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[4]: "area:extensions","area:sdk",authoring,dx
